Class MethodAnalyzer

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.bsc.dataclay.util.prefetchingspec.visitors.MethodAnalyzer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.ibm.wala.cast.ir.ssa.AstInstructionVisitor, com.ibm.wala.cast.java.ssa.AstJavaInstructionVisitor, com.ibm.wala.ssa.SSAInstruction.IVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ROPMethodAnalyzer
    public class MethodAnalyzer
extends Object
implements com.ibm.wala.cast.java.ssa.AstJavaInstructionVisitor
    A subclass of Wala's AstJavaInstructionVisitor that visits a method's instructions and extracts the information needed for prefetching.
